alter table "BC_InOutAdjust"

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_InOutAdjust" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_InOutAdjust"
(
"InOutAdjustID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32),
"StoreyID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR(20),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Status" INTEGER,
"IsAbolish" INTEGER,
"UpdateTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_BC_INOUTADJUST primary key ("InOutAdjustID")
);

comment on column "BC_InOutAdjust"."Status" is
'10:进撤场
20:合同创建
30:已取消（合同取消）
40:已有效（合同生效）
50:已废除（方案废除）';

alter table "BC_InOutAdjust"
add constraint FK_BC_INOUT_REFERENCE_BC_BOOTH foreign key (BCID)
references "BC_BoothChange" (BCID);
